    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but you said the dangers are \"often overstated\"... that sounds like you're taking a side. shouldn't we be more worried about how it leads to conflict and xenophobia? it feels like the \"social cohesion\" part is just an excuse for some pretty bad stuff.",
